high_descs: Turn right and face the counter.
Pick up the lettuce on the counter.
Turn right and then right again when you get to the counter, headed to the fridge.
Place the lettuce in the fridge to the left of the pot. Close the door, wait a moment, and take it out again.
Turn left and walk to the sink on the right counter.
Place the lettuce on the counter to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled head of lettuce on a counter.

high_descs: Move to the right facing the lettuce on the counter
Pick up the lettuce on top of the counter
Carry the lettuce to the white fridge to the right of the counter
Place the lettuce in the fridge then open the fridge and remove lettuce
Carry the lettuce to the left counter top next to the sink
Place the lettuce on top of the counter to the left of the sink
anns.task_desc: Chill a head of lettuce then place on the counter

high_descs: Take a step forward, then turn right and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the head of lettuce off of the counter.
Turn right and walk over to the sink, then turn right and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and put the head of lettuce inside, then close the fridge door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and remove the head of lettuce.
Turn left and walk towards the counter, then turn right to face the sink.
Put the chilled head of lettuce on the counter to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled head of lettuce on the counter.
